snippet: Ana Tijoux, of Chile, and Danay Suárez, of Cuba, performed as part of the Latin Alternative Music Conference.
abstract: Jon Pareles reviews performances by Ana Tijoux and Danay Suarez as part of 15th annual Latin Alternative Music Conference, series of free concerts at venues around New York City.
